<br>
It is very easy to kill all HG's in sight, especially if you have an epic pet.<br>
<br>
Remember to assist the HG's, to make sure you don't KS.<br>
<br>
Don't use a bolt to pull with, because then you can pull from outside the range where assist works and you will likely KS.<br>
<br>
Try to kill one HG at a time, even if the pet easily can kill 2 or 3 at at time.<br>
<br>
Kill place holders, that is lizardmen, basilisks, Cyclops and giant skelletons, because if there are a lot of active HG's, you will get less complaints. <br>
<br>
Did I mention not to KS?<br>
<br>
Try and assist people who are in trubble.<br>
<br>
